      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah those fees definitely suck. but even without the fees, it just feels like there's this invisible force working against me. like i put $300 in and it feels like only $50 actually counts towards the debt. it's almost like these hidden things are actively sabotaging my payments. how can a math formula be so predatory like that?",
